        ]
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "1. His word and counsel, to direct and guide them in the right way, which he oft mentions here as a singular blessing, ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "bld",
        "text": "Psalm 25:8,9,12",
        "children": [
